headline: Teledyne Deepens Subsea Autonomy Push With M Subs And Reson Milestones
summary: Teledyne Technologies (NYSE:TDY) has signed a Memorandum of Understanding with M Subs to collaborate on unmanned underwater vehicle development for naval and commercial use. Teledyne Marine's RESON brand is marking its 50th anniversary with new product launches showcased at the Oceanology International event. The announcements highlight Teledyne's focus on subsea technology and integrated marine solutions across defense and commercial markets. For you as an investor, these updates are...
